utton\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rch1665702606837.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rch1665702606837.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rch1665702606837.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rch1665702606837\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Printing Character Sets\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rch1665702606837__printing_character_sets_94283\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">To print, choose the device translation table that is specific for the character set.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rch1665702606837__p_d28919e1_d28920e1_d28921e1\">The following table shows examples of installable character sets and their corresponding device translation tables.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Device translation tables available for installable character sets</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Installable character set\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n Enhanced printing\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n Normal printing\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n English\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Central European\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_1250\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_1250\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Cyrillic\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_1251\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_1251\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Arabic\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_1256, P_MSWINX_AIX\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_1256,P_MSWIN3_AIX\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Greek\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_1253\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_1253\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Hebrew\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_1255\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_1255\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Simplified Chinese\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_GB\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_GB\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Korean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_KSC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_KSC\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Japanese\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX_SJIS, P_MSWINX_SJIS_1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3_SJIS, P_MSWIN3_SJIS_1\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__1\">\n Traditional Chinese\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__2\">\n P_MSWINX\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rch1665702606837__table_d2978e1_d2979e1_d2980e1__entry__3\">\n P_MSWIN3\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rch1665702606837__p_d28922e1_d28923e1_d28924e1\">For Arabic and Hebrew support, additional functionality is provided by the assignment setting <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gns1665702606915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gns1665702606915.html\" title=\"Determine processing required when printing right-to-left fields.\">$RTL_PRINTING</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531525\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Printing Character Sets Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Printing Character Sets To print, choose the device translation table that is specific for the character set. The following table shows examples of installable character sets and their corresponding device translation tables. Table 1. Device translation tables available for installable character sets Installable character set Enhanced printing Normal printing English P_MSWINX P_MSWIN3 Central European P_MSWINX_1250 P_MSWIN3_1250 Cyrillic P_MSWINX_1251 P_MSWIN3_1251 Arabic P_MSWINX_1256, P_MSWINX_AIX P_MSWIN3_1256,P_MSWIN3_AIX Greek P_MSWINX_1253 P_MSWIN3_1253 Hebrew P_MSWINX_1255 P_MSWIN3_1255 Simplified Chinese P_MSWINX_GB P_MSWIN3_GB Korean P_MSWINX_KSC P_MSWIN3_KSC Japanese P_MSWINX_SJIS, P_MSWINX_SJIS_1 P_MSWIN3_SJIS, P_MSWIN3_SJIS_1 Traditional Chinese P_MSWINX P_MSWIN3 For Arabic and Hebrew support, additional functionality is provided by the assignment setting $RTL_PRINTING . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}